{"tid":2257312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"｜港星旅遊氣泡在即 新加坡樟宜機場爆出兩員工確診","createTime":"2020-10-25T05:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T05:43:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"23299cf1708e6af53f8afedf058fc48f480348e7","tid":2257312,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:02:26.000Z","msg":"新加坡衞生部周六公佈，14宗新增武漢肺炎個案中，有兩名患者是樟宜機場三號客運大樓工作人員，當局正安排三號客運大樓可能接觸到旅客的工作人員接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n樟宜機場兩名確診工作人員分別是64歲的保安和48歲的體溫測量和拭子檢測助理，兩人並無接觸，在入院確診前都曾上班。保安員曾到過新加坡全國眼科中心 （Singapore National Eye Centre）治療本身的疾病，二人都是在看病期間發現有呼吸道感染病徵，然後接受檢測確診，目前未找到關聯病例。<br />\n<br />\n衞生部表示，將安排同一大樓可能接觸旅客的員工接受病毒檢測，又指預計未來數月，旅客量會增加，當局正考慮加強樟宜機場前線人員進行輪流定期檢測，日後會提供詳情。另外，當局指患者曾到過的地方是三號客運大樓內的「FairPrice Finest」和裕廊坊（Jurong Point）。"},{"pid":"71f68e024a17ca377b9b5ae4943d553ea6fe90e7","tid":2257312,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:04:38.000Z","msg":"開關開關"},{"pid":"8fd6653cee7df790322ef00cf41489600bdf667e","tid":2257312,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c251b5d82d33a1e447d379e18311e02348fbcc","tid":2257312,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"Let me innnnnn"},{"pid":"9c75390025a1279f19ff418f6b905373d211ec0e","tid":2257312,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"Monkey sick again<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=